==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Germination
<hw>Ger`mi*na"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>germinatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>germination</ets>.]</ety> <def>The
process of germinating; the beginning of vegetation or growth in a seed
or plant; the first development of germs, either animal or
vegetable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Germination apparatus</b></col>, <cd>an apparatus for
malting grain.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Germinative</ent>⟦br⟧
